articles.title: THEOS-2 Airbus-built satellite for Thailand successfully launched - Travel Daily
articles.description: The Airbus-built THEOS-2 Earth observation satellite has been successfully launched on a Vega rocket from Kourou, Europe’s spaceport in French Guiana.
